{"tid":1061862,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"膽固醇會導致口臭？","createTime":"2019-03-14T16:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T11:48:49.000Z","uid":138588,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7bf05533a5c6fd92b4f3f5206e27a8343f6d8b3d","tid":1061862,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"話說公司body check 驗到有膽固醇過高 其他正常，fit<br />\n小小個人資料 180cm 66kg<br />\n平時會飲食表面幾健康 一日三餐 冇零食 菜魚肉生果都有<br />\n點解會膽固醇高呢 可能係因為日日唔係雞翼就係排骨做夜餐<br />\n平時好介意口臭 有用開牙線 冇牙石 <br />\n試過刻意唔食肉一日三餐都食清淡 多菜少肉 睇中醫等都解決唔到<br />\n但膽固醇有得理 食麥皮<br />\n如是者食咗兩星期蕉奶麥皮做早餐 其他兩餐都盡量高脂肪野<br />\n結果口臭問題好似冇咗 個心都好似冇咁容易緊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇高手解答"},{"pid":"00237e7960aaebb3e6224628b058d2bd8f51ed47","tid":1061862,"uid":138588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"另外 果種口氣係由氣管谷出黎 唔係牙齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c95786a904113ffe8447df803969eb9db120e0","tid":1061862,"uid":35920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺結石"},{"pid":"b49fbf89f0b36b41d0861e669c8ec93d87dd9616","tid":1061862,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c95786a904113ffe8447df803969eb9db120e0","tid":1061862,"uid":35920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺結石"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好健康"},{"pid":"099ccb9288972b450a1adc2cc2579bf7e72ed596","tid":1061862,"uid":42673,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:58:24.000Z","msg":"多數便秘會口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長時間唔食嘢個口都會特別臭"},{"pid":"65841450e096d20fcff8a28762b6a3a4ad789de6","tid":1061862,"uid":138588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"099ccb9288972b450a1adc2cc2579bf7e72ed596","tid":1061862,"uid":42673,"like":3,"